channel.title: New to 508, I need to know something
channel.description:
Hello, Incognito here, I am new to coding 508 servers, and I can't seem to find a client.java? Or, where do I edit the login text, when you log in it will say like "Welcome to RuneScape".
I would really appreciate your help. ~Incognito~
